verses.verse: A Psalm of David. Ascribe<WH3051> unto Jehovah<WH3068>, O ye sons of the mighty<WH1121>, Ascribe<WH3051> unto Jehovah<WH3068> glory<WH3519> and strength<WH5797>.
Ascribe <WH3051> unto Jehovah<WH3068> the glory<WH3519> due unto his name<WH8034>; Worship<WH7812> Jehovah<WH3068> in holy<WH6944> array<WH1927>.
The voice<WH6963> of Jehovah<WH3068> is upon the waters<WH4325>: The God<WH410> of glory<WH3519> thundereth<WH7481>, Even Jehovah<WH3068> upon many<WH7227> waters<WH4325>.
The voice<WH6963> of Jehovah<WH3068> is powerful<WH3581>; The voice<WH6963> of Jehovah<WH3068> is full of majesty<WH1926>.
The voice<WH6963> of Jehovah<WH3068> breaketh<WH7665> the cedars<WH730>; Yea<WH3068>, Jehovah breaketh<WH7665> in pieces the cedars<WH730> of Lebanon<WH3844>.
He maketh them also to skip<WH7540> like a calf<WH5695>; Lebanon<WH3844> and Sirion<WH8303> like a young<WH1121> wild-ox<WH7214>.
The voice<WH6963> of Jehovah<WH3068> cleaveth<WH2672> the flames<WH3852> of fire<WH784>.
The voice<WH6963> of Jehovah<WH3068> shaketh<WH2342> the wilderness<WH4057>; Jehovah<WH3068> shaketh<WH2342> the wilderness<WH4057> of Kadesh<WH6946>.
The voice<WH6963> of Jehovah<WH3068> maketh the hinds<WH355> to calve<WH2342>, And strippeth<WH2834> the forests<WH3295> bare<WH1964>: And in his temple everything saith<WH559>, Glory<WH3519>.
Jehovah <WH3068> sat<WH3427> as King at the Flood<WH3999>; Yea<WH3068>, Jehovah sitteth<WH3427> as King<WH4428> for ever<WH5769>.
Jehovah <WH3068> will give<WH5414> strength<WH5797> unto his people<WH5971>; Jehovah<WH3068> will bless<WH1288> his people<WH5971> with peace<WH7965>.
